sudo nmap -sS -sU --top-ports 100 -T4 --open -iL targets.txt -oN Scan_result.txt



-sS: TCP SYN scan

-sU: UDP scan

--top-ports 100: Scan top 100 common ports (faster than all 65535)

--open: Only show hosts with open ports

-iL targets.txt: Read targets from a file

-oN open_ports.txt: Output to a readable text file
